title: Fix TH compile warnings
body_html: Compiling from scratch prints a lot of warnings from TH files, making it impossible to identify which one is the error that stops compilation. Most of these warnings are unused variables, and comparing signed and unsigned types. This PR fixes all of compile warnings except for unknown pragma, which is suppressed via -Wno-unknown-pragmas.

body: Compiling from scratch prints a lot of warnings from TH files, making it impossible to identify which one is the error that stops compilation. Most of these warnings are unused variables, and comparing signed and unsigned types. This PR fixes all of compile warnings except for unknown pragma, which is suppressed via `-Wno-unknown-pragmas`.
